{"tid":2311317,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Danny 仔孔德賢處男TVB新劇 《香港愛情故事》下周一首播","createTime":"2020-12-04T03:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T03:44:37.000Z","uid":240918,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f76e605e4e84860dd3c154ea389516dbca55327c","tid":2311317,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"《香港愛情故事》羅天宇、龔嘉欣連場床戰<br />\n<br />\n今次已經係無綫2020年第二度臨急變陣（對上一次是9月出晒宣傳後抽起《唐人街》換成《C9特工》），《香港愛情故事》係新晉監製林肯的首作品，他希望透過這套作品，講述香港不同年齡層的愛情故事，從中反映香港人在社會、土地、相處等所遇上的問題。《香港愛情故事》由羅天宇、龔嘉欣及王敏奕領銜主演，並由謝東閔、龔慈恩、白彪、石修及游嘉欣聯合演出，並由蔣家旻，梁証嘉及孔德賢特別演出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDU3hDv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDU3hDv.jpg&h=1ed52038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/howATeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhowATeE.jpg&h=43dbaaa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫新劇《香港愛情故事》昨晚11月30日推出預告片，並將於<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">下周一12月7日</span></span>起安排在<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">晚上10點半</span></span>首播，因每集1小時，《晚間新聞》被迫讓路，延後半小時至11點半播出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbqYQ1p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbqYQ1p.png&h=325d2276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下周一10點半就有Danny 仔首套TVB新劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n戲中激戰連場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n噴血演出一個又一個香港愛情故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n包保大家睇到面紅耳赤，浴火焚身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n大家點可以錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047799bcc71f0fe2d87397c123b53a29b2da0fb8","tid":2311317,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"個垃圾第三者!"},{"pid":"8dcff62bf892d7b4a07